snippet.title: LET IT DIE - E32016 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Published by GungHo Online Entertainment and developed by Grasshopper Manufacture, LET IT DIE is an upcoming free-to-play survival action game. Death cancels everything, except the truth. #letitdiethegame

This particular gameplay footage was unveiled during E32016. Enjoy!

http://www.letitdiethegame.com/
